WEBVTT

00:00.360 --> 00:01.850
Previously on "Salem"...

00:03.266 --> 00:04.895
You're free of my son,

00:04.920 --> 00:06.614
but his brother is still here.

00:06.654 --> 00:07.739
Come Black Sunday,

00:07.764 --> 00:10.364
my true brothers will rise from hell

00:10.389 --> 00:11.809
and stand beside me.

00:11.834 --> 00:13.028
This is his weapon.

00:13.053 --> 00:15.161
Red Mercury. I
want nothing of it.

00:15.186 --> 00:16.778
I have others to think of.

00:16.803 --> 00:18.028
My baby.

00:18.053 --> 00:19.231
Cotton's baby.

00:19.256 --> 00:20.684
You're asking me to marry you.

00:20.709 --> 00:22.450
This business of love.

00:22.475 --> 00:24.239
All this must be one.

00:24.264 --> 00:26.278
But there remains one obstacle.

00:26.303 --> 00:27.883
Isaac.

00:27.908 --> 00:29.217
No tears.

00:29.272 --> 00:31.825
You are the luckiest girl I know.

00:31.850 --> 00:33.708
Everything you
need to kill an angel.

00:33.733 --> 00:36.864
You must forge a dagger with that in it

00:36.889 --> 00:38.919
and kill him with the dagger.

00:38.944 --> 00:41.403
You can do
whatever you want to me.

00:41.428 --> 00:43.434
- Just not here.
- Yes.

00:43.459 --> 00:46.020
Alden will most likely think
it all a dream in the morning,

00:46.045 --> 00:47.637
but he'll never forget what he has seen.

00:47.662 --> 00:49.155
What lies beyond that door?

00:49.180 --> 00:52.377
Beyond that
door lies hell itself.

